itions#Winger|Winger]]\n|align=center| 19\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|London Broncos|size=12}} London Broncos Academy\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center|'''28'''\n|align=center| [[Morgan Smith (rugby league)|Morgan Smith]]\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Scrum Half|Scrum Half]]\n|align=center| {{Age|df=yes|1998|4|30}}\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|Warrington Wolves|size=12}} [[Warrington Wolves]]\n|align=center| 17\n|align=center| 1\n|align=center| 3\n|align=center| 2\n|align=center| 12\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center|'''29'''\n|align=center| [[Matt Davis (rugby league)|Matt Davis]] {{Efn|No longer at the club}}\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Loose Forward|Loose Forward]]\n|align=center|  {{Age|1996|7|5|df=y}}\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|Warrington Wolves|size=12}} [[Warrington Wolves]] (Loan)\n|align=center| 4\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center|'''30'''\n|align=center| [[Olsi Krasniqi]] \n|align=center|{{flagicon|ALB}}\n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Prop|Prop]]\n|align=center| {{Age|df=yes|1992|6|28}}\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|Toronto Wolfpack|size=12}} [[Toronto Wolfpack]] \n|align=center| 9\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center|'''31'''\n|align=center| [[Brock Lamb]] \n|align=center|{{flagicon|AUS}}\n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Scrum Half|Scrum Half]]\n|align=center| {{Age|df=yes|1997|1|22}}\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|Sydney Roosters|size=12}} [[Sydney Roosters]] \n|align=center| 6\n|align=center| 3\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 1\n|align=center| 13\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center|'''32'''\n|align=center| [[Guy Armitage]] \n|align=center|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Wing|Wing]]\n|align=center| {{Age|1991|11|29|df=y}}\n|align=center| [[Ealing Trailfinders Rugby Club]] \n|align=center| 2\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|align=center| 0\n|}\n;Notes\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Tale of the Tape==\n\n''Most Points in a Game'' \n*'''18''', Round 15: [[Kieran Dixon]] vs. [[Wakefield Trinity]] (2 tries and 5 goals)\n\n''Most tries in a Game''\n*'''4''', Round 15: [[Jordan Abdull]] vs. [[Wakefield Trinity]]\n\n''Highest score in a winning game''\n*'''42''', Round 1: vs. [[Wakefield Trinity]] & Round 15: vs. [[Wakefield Trinity]]\n\n''Lowest score in a winning game''\n*'''17''', Round 26: vs. [[Catalans Dragons]]\n\n''Greatest winning margin''\n*'''20,''' Round 23: vs. [[St Helens R.F.C.|St. Helens]]\n\n''Greatest number of games won consecutively''\n*'''3''', Round 17 to Round 19\n\n''Highest score in a losing game''\n*'''28''', Round 24: vs. [[Salford Red Devils]]\n\n''Lowest score in a losing game''\n*'''0''', Round 2: vs. [[Salford Red Devils]], Round 5: vs. [[St Helens R.F.C.|St. Helens]]\n\n''Greatest losing margin''\n*'''36''', Round 9: vs. [[Warrington Wolves]]\n\n''Greatest number of games lost consecutively''\n*'''8''', Round 7 to Round 14. Includes the defeat at [[Halifax R.L.F.C.]] in [[Challenge Cup]] Round 5, but excludes Round 10 reversal at [[Hull Kingston Rovers]] which was brought forward and played after Round 2.\n\n==Transfers==\n\n===In===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"  style=\"width:70%; font-size:85%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n!width=5%|Country\n!width=30%|Name\n!!width=30%|Position\n!width=20%|Signed from\n!width=25%|Date\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center| {{flagicon|Wales|rugby league}}\n|align=center| [[Matty Fozard]] \n|align=center| [[Rugby league positions#Hooker|Hooker]]\n|align=center| {{leagueicon|Sheffield Eagles|12}}[[Sheffield Eagles]]\n|align=center| October 2018\n|- style=\"background:#fff;\"\n|align=center| {{flagicon|ENG|rugby le